{
  "texts": [
    "They devised various feature templates to support these tasks, including word features, part-of-speech features, dependency relation features, word distance features, and sentiment features.",
    "In crossdomain aspect extraction tasks, it emphasizes the challenges in performing cross-domain aspect extraction.",
    "Opinion words in different domains may exhibit differing sentiment tendencies, and the substantial differences in aspect vocabularies across domains make crossdomain aspect extraction particularly complex.",
    "This task involves identifying the category to which the aspect term belongs.",
    "In this example, the aspect category is \"battery.\""
  ]
}